*Who was the job offered?
*The job wasn't offered Max, it was offered Harry. *The tuba was given John Phillips Sousa.
I will offer two ways of treating this phenomenon without choosing between them. In the first, we postulate a cliti- cization or restructuring rule which optionally incorporates the first of two noun phrases to the right of the verb (if it is a definite pronoun) in s-uch a way as to make a single
177

 constituent of the verb and pronoun. This rule is written:
16) Cliticization:
